    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Poison is Served!</strong> - a cozy balancing puzzle with management elements and satiric narrative. You play an ancient roman food taster who works in the Emperor's palace. Every day you need to taste poisoned food, analyze how it affects your health, plan the order of tasting and try to survive at the end of day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/c85c9d4549f78f73ccfec6e20b150252.poster.avif?t=1770050692\" width=660 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/c85c9d4549f78f73ccfec6e20b150252.webm?t=1770050692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/c85c9d4549f78f73ccfec6e20b150252.mp4?t=1770050692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Numerous poisoned food combinations</strong>. All food in this world is poisoned and your challenge is to identify how it works to staying alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/600a355f6027049b86d9c1b48cb18671.webp?t=1770050692\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/600a355f6027049b86d9c1b48cb18671.poster.avif?t=1770050692\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meet your colleagues and make friends. Or not?</strong> Up to 10 unique characters who provide specific mechanics to make the taster's life a little bit easier. Solve their tasks, take part in palace intrigues, choose sides and change the fate of the whole Empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/683c76f9af6c366a437b4fbeb4aa875a.poster.avif?t=1770050692\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011050/extras/683c76f9af6c366a437b4fbeb4aa875a.webm?t=1770050692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And much more:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy mini games like Poisoner device where you can craft your own poison from food scraps at the end of day</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Palace Court with independent live simulation that reflect and develop by players decisions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous funny and satiric stories and quests.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
